00038 //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
00039 // Function: find()
00040 //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
00041 MCAPIFunctionDesc const* MCAPIFunctionSet::find(QString const& name) const
00042 {
00043     QList<MCAPIFunctionDesc>::const_iterator itrFunc = m_functions.begin();
00044 
00045     while (itrFunc != m_functions.end())
00046     {
00047         if (itrFunc->getName() == name)
00048         {
00049             return &(*itrFunc);
00050         }
00051 
00052         ++itrFunc;
00053     }
00054 
00055     return 0;
00056 }

00068 //-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
00069 MCAPIFunctionDesc* MCAPIFunctionSet::addFunctionDesc(QString const& name, VariableType returnType,
00070                                                      QString const& returnHint)
00071 {
00072     Q_ASSERT(find(name) == 0);
00073 
00074     m_functions.push_back(MCAPIFunctionDesc(name, returnType, returnHint));
00075     return &m_functions.back();
00076 }
